videos.headline: Texas picks off Gerry Bohanon on second play of the game
videos.description: Baylor turns the ball over on the opening drive as B.J. Foster makes the interception and returns it to the Bears' 31-yard line.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas picks off Gerry Bohanon on second play of the game) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Joshua Moore hauls in a 10-yard TD pass for Texas
videos.description: Casey Thompson finds Joshua Moore in the end zone as the Longhorns strike early against Baylor.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Joshua Moore hauls in a 10-yard TD pass for Texas) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor reaches into its bag of tricks for a TD
videos.description: Baylor runs a modified Philly Special, as WR Tyquan Thornton throws a TD pass to R.J. Sneed.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor reaches into its bag of tricks for a TD) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Xavier Worthy left wide open on 63-yard Texas TD
videos.description: Casey Thompson airs it out to Xavier Worthy, who makes the catch in stride and strolls into the end zone for the Longhorns.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Xavier Worthy left wide open on 63-yard Texas TD) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor, Texas trade interceptions in final seconds of first half
videos.description: Baylor QB Gerry Bohanon gifts Texas prime field position, just for Casey Thompson to get picked off a few seconds later.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor, Texas trade interceptions in final seconds of first half) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bijan Robinson scores a TD in his 10th straight game for Texas
videos.description: Bijan Robinson scores from the 1-yard line to extend Texas' lead at Baylor.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bijan Robinson scores a TD in his 10th straight game for Texas) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gerry Bohanon runs in for a 6-yard TD
videos.description: Baylor QB Gerry Bohanon keeps it himself and finds his way into the end zone for the Bears.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gerry Bohanon runs in for a 6-yard TD) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor TE catches Texas off guard with rushing TD
videos.description: Tight end Ben Sims sweeps around and carries in a 1-yard touchdown to give Baylor the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor TE catches Texas off guard with rushing TD) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Abram Smith spins out of a tackle, breaks off 32-yard TD run
videos.description: Baylor RB Abram Smith shakes a tackle with a spin move and races away to the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NFC_One-Play (Abram Smith spins out of a tackle, breaks off 32-yard TD run) 2021/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor fights back to hand Texas third straight loss
videos.description: No. 16 Baylor comes from behind to beat Texas 31-24 in Waco.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Baylor fights back to hand Texas third straight loss) 2021/10/30 ESHEET
